ff21e81cec","tid":1453822,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲唔孝敬班警察屋企人仲等乜呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"227d27bca9807579d33e1003e024c85e088e63e0","tid":1453822,"uid":79085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"所有銀行都要㩒啦<br />\n冇存款 銀行冇借比公司 不合作運動"},{"pid":"2c3b7c314e4686ec39376bb4016e8bfcf0f84158","tid":1453822,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"重新整理<br />\n<br />\n<strong>前線良心記者<br />\n求你哋連成一線，接力問落去<br />\n畀佢哋遊走咗，下一位就follow up question繼續問<br />\n呢啲係我哋最關心嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n每日無論邊個問先，頭幾條都要係呢幾條！！<br />\n每一次問都數， 呢條問題係第幾次第幾日問，未有答案！ 幾時先會有答案？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請準備好每條問題嘅影片及圖片<br />\n準備播放器，迫使cctvb要播<br />\n佢一路拒絕播嘅畫面出街</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 721點解唔執法？點解只告非法集會？點解全部未落charge？<br />\n播圖播片<br />\n指揮官喺村公所同白衣人對話，當時佢哋手持武器， 點解唔執法？<br />\n播片<br />\n<br />\n2 有證據顯示警方用過期Tear Gas?用咗幾多?點解用?<br />\n請準備圖及片<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n過期催淚彈 成分變質變山埃， 警方會否道歉及賠償？<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察係咪扮示威者，然後執法？ 點解用咁嘅策略 ？ 點證明 冇掉磚？冇煽動？冇放火？會否Charge佢哋參與暴動?<br />\n準備圖及片<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解會係地鐵站 內放催淚彈同胡椒彈？目的係驅趕定拘捕？<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n8. 頭部嚴重受傷，明顯見到一灘血喺地面，已被制服，完全冇反抗能力，哭求唔好撳， 點解仲要惡意跪喺個頭上面？ 因為仇恨？因為唔識聽廣東話？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/703181869/posts/10157404127116870?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F703181869%2Fposts%2F10157404127116870%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=2b44bcec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/703181869/posts/10157404127116870?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n問呢條嘅目的係煽情，同埋尋日條片畀cctvb剪咗<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=85c444f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=b86d1b47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=25a47214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424974427599276&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=6b4e53c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424